1
00:00:21,516 --> 00:00:28,198
[SPEAKER_01]: Hello, everyone, and welcome to Medford Happenings, a show for and about the city of Medford.

2
00:00:29,238 --> 00:00:44,963
[SPEAKER_01]: I am John Petrella, and the purpose of this program is to give Medford citizens facts and information to help you make informed choices.

3
00:00:46,253 --> 00:00:53,679
[SPEAKER_01]: and to discover city services or businesses that you may not have been aware of.

4
00:00:58,102 --> 00:01:09,211
[SPEAKER_01]: And our guests today are Marie Cassidy and Irina Shumway, who are from the Method Family Network.

5
00:01:10,612 --> 00:01:11,693
[SPEAKER_01]: And I want to welcome

6
00:01:13,022 --> 00:01:20,130
