23
00:02:00,950 --> 00:02:02,913
[SPEAKER_03]: Well, I'm born and raised, I'm a MEFA girl.

24
00:02:03,153 --> 00:02:05,516
[SPEAKER_03]: I'm a MEFA girl, born and raised in Medford.

25
00:02:06,338 --> 00:02:06,898
[SPEAKER_03]: Attended St.

