27
00:02:13,167 --> 00:02:18,209
[SPEAKER_03]: I had a wonderful opportunity to become one of the first Park Department leaders in Medford.

28
00:02:18,869 --> 00:02:25,231
[SPEAKER_03]: And what happened to me was I, it was called the Waite School at the time, up at the top of Fall?

29
00:02:25,451 --> 00:02:25,851
[SPEAKER_03]: Yes.

30
00:02:26,091 --> 00:02:30,993
[SPEAKER_03]: A very small school, but I was given the opportunity to start this whole new program.

31
00:02:31,053 --> 00:02:36,935
[SPEAKER_03]: I was 16, and I had a bunch of parents and children came, and I immediately fell in love

32
00:02:37,675 --> 00:02:41,258
[SPEAKER_03]: and I knew from then on what I wanted to do with my life.

33
00:02:41,358 --> 00:02:51,027
