35
00:02:58,713 --> 00:03:08,356
[SPEAKER_03]: the Head Start director, Head Start teacher, a social worker, and worked with the Office for Children, doing a lot of work for families and children, and I've always just loved doing that.

36
00:03:09,196 --> 00:03:12,657
