95
00:06:52,476 --> 00:06:58,779
[SPEAKER_03]: And I'm sitting in my unit with my supervisor, and a call came in from a person by the name of Roy Belson.

96
00:06:59,799 --> 00:07:04,602
[SPEAKER_03]: And he wanted to talk with someone about starting this new program.

97
00:07:05,242 --> 00:07:10,705
