[SPEAKER_00]: We don't ask any questions.

162
00:11:11,008 --> 00:11:16,433
[SPEAKER_00]: Um, we don't have anybody fill anything out to, to qualify for anything we offer.

163
00:11:16,793 --> 00:11:23,099
[SPEAKER_00]: The only criteria is they have to live or work in Medford and to have at least one child from birth to eight.

164
00:11:23,579 --> 00:11:26,482
[SPEAKER_00]: And that's because of our, uh, grant sponsors.

165
00:11:27,102 --> 00:11:30,906
[SPEAKER_00]: And so some of the things that we offer, we offer, uh, play and learn groups.

166
00:11:31,486 --> 00:11:32,407
[SPEAKER_00]: And a lot of them are,

