168
00:11:47,192 --> 00:11:59,315
[SPEAKER_00]: And what's important about that, too, is we prioritize kids who are not currently in a preschool environment, not in a structured setting, so that gives them a leg up, hopefully, by the time they go and register and enter kindergarten.

