[SPEAKER_03]: You can look at our calendar to see when we're open, every day of those seven days.

357
00:26:40,875 --> 00:26:50,780
[SPEAKER_03]: Come on down and set up a meeting with Irina or I or Heather or Andrea, any of our staff, to sit down and talk about those opportunities.

358
00:26:51,600 --> 00:26:52,321
[SPEAKER_03]: We welcome that.

359
00:26:52,821 --> 00:26:58,023
[SPEAKER_00]: And if somebody is not able to donate, we do a lot of events where we need people to help.

